{"tid":1687430,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［重要！］11.2今日目的唔係撚狗！請無視佢哋！","createTime":"2019-11-01T23:03:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T23:34:48.000Z","uid":313646,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7fa866018f79735411c8b49353fef4e4fc52287b","tid":1687430,"uid":313646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T23:03:35.000Z","msg":"太多太多次每當我哋行到狗身邊就鬧狗撚狗，結果大家有目共睹，係咪都舉旗話人非法集結、子彈放題tg放題！<br />\n<br />\n今日好多人冇裝，唔好畀位佢哋入，經過請無視佢哋，<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">嗌返我哋嘅訴求！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">記得你出街嘅目的！並不是撚狗！</span>唔想任何一個人畀狗咬！<br />\n<br />\n佢哋未開始就搜身、9拉，記住喺公眾地方講嘢小心啲！盡可能<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">唔好搭黨鐵</span></span>！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">食飽飽有力行，盡情懲罰黃店！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81c00bb622664fa16450da38de0831e3a7622dfd","tid":1687430,"uid":89557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T23:08:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51f2573916f8820486b7f462dbf53e7688b63e6d","tid":1687430,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T23:20:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/77uBc81.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F77uBc81.gif&h=5ceee803&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0171233ce87a959543f2e77fb4a703023453615d","tid":1687430,"uid":187755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T23:34:48.000Z","msg":"其實撚唔撚狗都照舉旗和話你非法集結<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}